column2: ANOTHER READING THIS DATE WAS NOT CORRECT.  IT WAS 4.5 FEET AND SHOULD HAVE BEEN 1.2 FEET.
WATER CLEARED FROM 1.2' TO 4.2' READING IN A WEEK.  HAD ABOUT 1/5 - 2" RAIN BETWEEN READINGS.
water clarity reading increased 8' since last reading.  Algae die off probably due to many cloudy days.  Could see most of the bottom around the lake.
